English(en): Thanks for playing the demo.  Continue your escape from hell in the full game.  Thats it for now!

Chinese (Simplified)(zh-Hans): Early soil untouched by water. Passive increase to {basePlayerStats.critChance} critical chance and {basePlayerStats.dodge} dodge.
The dictionary of demons. Passively gain {basePlayerStats.nimbusesDamageBoost} disk damage, and {basePlayerStats.critChance} critical chance.
Sacred text of apocalyptic proportions. Passively gain {basePlayerStats.dodge} dodge, {basePlayerStats.luck} luck, and {basePlayerStats.critChance} critical chance.
Nails from the cross.  {chance}% chance on <color=#00e4ff>weapon hit</color> to splinter nails from your enemy which deal {damage.amount} damage.
Demon blood swirls.  Every {requiredCount} <color=#00e4ff>juggles</color> gain {statAtkSpeed}% attack speed for {duration} seconds.
A clay cylinder with inscriptions of a Babylonian king.  5%  increases  to attack speed on juggle.
A fragment of wood from  the cross.  Every {requiredCount} <color=#00e4ff>juggles</color> shoot a wave of splinters which deal {damage.amount} damage.
Frighten away evil with the twang of this string.  Increase luck by {playerStats.luck}% on each <color=#00e4ff>juggle</color> up to a stack of {maxCount} for the wave.
A scrap of cloth dripping with wine.  Start each wave with an active <color=#00e4ff>disk guard</color>.
An electrically charged tooth. On critical hit rain down a thunder shock to one random enemy dealing {damage.amount} damage.
An everlasting flame.  Upon <color=#00e4ff>cleanse</color> deal {damage.amount} damage every second to one random  enemy over {duration} seconds.
It is engulfed in flame but unburnt.   On <color=#00e4ff>disk hit</color> deal 1 damage every second  over  {dotDuration}  seconds.
Eternal light burns bright. <color=#00e4ff>On cleanse</color> gain {playerStats.nimbusesDamageBoost} disk damage untill the wave ends.

A bracelet of a serpent eating its tail. Gain {statAtkSpeed}% attack speed, {playerStats.critChance} critical chance,  and {playerStats.nimbusesDamageBoost} disk damage on cleanse for {duration}  seconds at the expense of 1 hp.
Connecting to the beyond. On enemy death gain {playerStats.critChance}% critical chance for that wave.
A branch from a tree which has jewels for leaves.  If no disk is lost during a wave heal to max hp.
A bone as hard as stone.  On <color=#00e4ff>disk spawn</color> untill a disk is lost, gain {playerStats.dodge}% dodge for {duration} seconds.
A bottomless cauldren.  On last heart heal for 3 breaking the cauldren.
An Impenetrable hide suitable for making armor.  Gain 100% dodge till first dodge.
A root from the tree of life.  {chance}% chance on disk loss to spawn a new disk immediately.
Repels the supernatural. On disk spawn damage all present enemies for {damage.amount} damage.
All life starts on the path of the sun. On disk loss all remaining disks shoot out rays of light which deal {damage.amount}.
A token for guidance. On dodge duplicate all disks.
A  wheel seen by Ezekiel. On cleanse fire a new disk.
A fragment of what killed the Titans.  On disk hit strike a random enemy with lightning which deals {damage.amount}, until a disk is lost.
It can burn even gods to ashes.  On Enemy Death {chance}% chance to fire a new disk.
A legendary signet ring, that seals demonic forces. On cleanse trigger an explosion which deals {damage.amount} at all disks.
A parchment that holds the secrets to all knowledge.   Spawns a ever present paddle that guards your disks.
A Bow gifted by the god of self-discipline armed with infallible arrows. A weapon which shoots heat seaking arrows which deal {damage.amount} damage
The holy spear that shared a great sacrifice. A weapon which shoots weaving energy which deal {damage.amount} damage.
A sling that was used to fell giants, and rattle armies. A fast shooting weapon which deals {damage.amount} damage.
A staff which emits the rays  of the sun. A direct damage weapon which shoots out rays of light which deal {damage.amount} damage.
A trident that severed the new beginnings. A three pronged weapon which shoots which deals {damage.amount} damage.
Paying a fare not for you.  For every {value} motes you have gain {statDamage}% bonus damage.
A lump of flesh that constantly regenerates. Heal {playerStats.currentHp} hit point at the end of a round.
Dew that falls from the World Tree.  On bounce {chance}% chance to spawn dew drop upon player hit replenish a cleanse.
The solar deity’s pure energy.  On juggle {chance}% chance to drop a chakra when picked cause an explosion at a random enemy which deals {damage.amount} damage.
Triton played to calm or raise the waves. On bounce {chance}% chance to apply a slight upwards force to all disks it hits.
A belt that grants thunder power.  Disk damage is increased by each disk hit by {playerStats.nimbusesDamageBoost} until a disk is lost.
A hammer used  to defeat Asag, a monstrous demon.
An axe used to cleave the world into existance. A slow firing weapon which penetrates enemies, dealing {damage.amount} damage.
A poison created from the sea when the gods and demons churned it to obtain Amrita.  On damage received loose all <color=#00e4ff>active disks</color>.
Given to each lost soul this brew induces instant and permanent amnesia.  On  <color=#00e4ff>disk loss</color> lose 1 cleanse.
Fruit of the Dead.  On <color=#00e4ff>disk loss</color> reduce luck by {playerStats.luck} for {duration} seconds.
The weight of the world on a ring.   Disk gravity is increased by {basePlayerStats.nibusGravity} permanently.
Temptation beyond all measure. On disk loss, if no other active disks exist take 1 damage.
A Skull cup used as a ritual implement.  Passive increase of {basePlayerStats.nimbusesDamageBoost} disk damage.

One of the seven braids of hair that gifted unbelievable strength.  Passive increase of {basePlayerStats.nimbusesDamageBoost} disk damage, {basePlayerStats.critChance} critical chance, and {baseDamage}% damage boost.
